modules.description: This module parses AWS configuration files into structured data, extracts values from JSON representations of configurations, and provides direct access to S3-related settings. It operates on strings, association lists, and Yojson.Safe.t trees, with support for named profiles. Functions like `get`, `(#.)`, and `read_file` retrieve specific configuration values or load entire files, while `s3` and related accessors target S3 endpoint settings directly.
